Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
